  "title": "docs(dev-novel): add tabs to switch between kinds of stories",
  "body": "This PR adds tabs on top of dev-novel so that we can easily switch between the different kinds of stories: built-in widgets, connectors + jQuery, unmountable widgets. Those stories were there, but you had to know the URL in order to access them.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1440\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-05-29 at 06 35 59\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/393765/40638349-20fa2c88-630b-11e8-8c9c-0a82d744fe12.png\">\r\n\r\nIt is [available on the preview](https://deploy-preview-2947--algolia-instantsearch.netlify.com/v2/dev-novel/?selectedStory=Analytics.default)",
